-- Iran Warns Importers Not to Hold Goods Due to Rial, Mehr Says
-- B y   L o u i s   M e i x l e r
-- 2012-01-16T08:23:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-16/iran-warns-importers-not-to-hold-goods-due-to-rial-mehr-says.html
Iranian importers who withhold sales
of goods due to a surge in the value of foreign currencies will
face “severe punishment,” the  state-run Mehr news agency  said,
citing Javad Taghavi, deputy chief of the Organization for the
Protection of Consumers and Producers.  To contact the reporter on this story:
